I'd like to make a prediction.

New first gank target for Lee / J4 / Shaco / Panth / Xin: the other jungler. They're the only ones in the current jungling set capable of a meaningful early gank with high HP, and now the KNOW the other guy is going to is going to have crappy health as he struggles to make 2 potions and no sustain last an extra camp.{{item:3070}} {{champion:32}} {{item:3070}} 

all of a sudden, those guys aren't just the dominant junglers: They're literally the only viable picks unless all 5 are banned at once.

Your jobs regarding the jungle would be a lot easier if you'd address the actual problem.

